      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEE THIS (1) is generally an honest type in the frame at 10 of 28 starts but missed the placings last time when fifth (29.76) over 520m at Richmond. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Drawn the rails and rates a key runner. RED ROCK RAZZLE (7) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Richmond over 520m behind Foreign Capital (29.91) in a NG. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can figure in the finish. MY CUPCAKE (4) was below best last time when fourth but prior to that was a Grade 5 winner in quick time at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. O'KEEFE (5) should be thereabouts after leading before collecting a minor prize most recently.",
